---
export const prerender = true;
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="How to Use xConvert24" description="Learn how to use xConvert24.com — a quick guide to unit converters, tools, search, bookmarks, dark mode and more." keywords="how to use, user guide, help, tutorial, conversion guide, xConvert24 help">
  <div class="max-w-3xl">
    <div class="mb-8">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
        <span class="text-3xl" aria-hidden="true">📖</span>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">How to Use xConvert24</h1>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">A quick guide to get the most out of our converters and tools.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <!-- Step 1: Converting units -->
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-6 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
          <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/30 text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-400 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">1</span>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Converting Units</h2>
        </div>
        <ol class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 ml-11 list-decimal">
          <li>Pick a converter from the sidebar menu or the homepage grid (e.g. Weight, Length, Temperature).</li>
          <li>Select the <strong>"From"</strong> unit using the dropdown (e.g. Kilograms).</li>
          <li>Enter a number in the input field.</li>
          <li>Select the <strong>"To"</strong> unit (e.g. Pounds).</li>
          <li>The result appears instantly — no need to press a button.</li>
          <li>Click <strong>Swap</strong> to reverse the conversion direction.</li>
        </ol>
        <div class="mt-3 ml-11 p-3 bg-amber-50 dark:bg-amber-900/10 rounded-lg text-xs text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-400">
          💡 <strong>Tip:</strong> The formula is shown below the result so you can see exactly how the calculation works.
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2: Using the search -->
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-6 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
          <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/30 text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-400 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">2</span>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Finding What You Need</h2>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 ml-11">
          <li>• Use the <strong>search bar</strong> in the top header — type a unit name, abbreviation, or category (e.g. "kg", "mph", "loan").</li>
          <li>• A dropdown shows matching results instantly. Click one to jump there.</li>
          <li>• Press <kbd class="px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded text-xs font-mono">/</kbd> on your keyboard to focus the search from anywhere on the site.</li>
          <li>• On mobile, tap the 🔍 icon in the header.</li>
          <li>• The sidebar has a collapsible <strong>treeview</strong> — click a category to expand or collapse it.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3: Tools -->
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-6 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
          <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/30 text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-400 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">3</span>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Calculators & Tools</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 ml-11 mb-3">Beyond unit conversion, we have specialised calculators:</p>
        <div class="ml-11 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          <div>🔭 <a href="/tools/calculator" class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 hover:underline">Scientific Calculator</a> — trig, log, powers</div>
          <div>🧍 <a href="/tools/bmi" class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 hover:underline">BMI Calculator</a> — body mass index</div>
          <div>🎨 <a href="/tools/color" class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 hover:underline">Color Picker</a> — RGB/HEX/HSL/CMYK</div>
          <div>🏦 <a href="/tools/loan" class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 hover:underline">Loan Calculator</a> — payments & amortization</div>
          <div>🍽️ <a href="/tools/tip" class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 hover:underline">Tip Calculator</a> — split bills</div>
          <div>🏷️ <a href="/tools/discount" class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 hover:underline">Discount Calculator</a> — sale prices</div>
          <div>🎂 <a href="/tools/age" class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 hover:underline">Age Calculator</a> — exact age from DOB</div>
          <div>📅 <a href="/tools/date-diff" class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 hover:underline">Date Difference</a> — days between dates</div>
          <div>🌍 <a href="/tools/clock" class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 hover:underline">World Clock</a> — 12 cities live</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 4: Dark mode & bookmarks -->
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-6 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
          <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/30 text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-400 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">4</span>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Personalization</h2>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 ml-11">
          <li>• <strong>Dark / Light mode:</strong> Click the 🌙/☀️ icon in the top-right. Your preference is remembered.</li>
          <li>• <strong>Bookmark pages:</strong> Click the 🔖 icon to save a converter for quick access. Bookmarks are stored in your browser.</li>
          <li>• <strong>Cookie preferences:</strong> Click the 🍪 icon in the bottom-left to manage analytics and marketing cookies.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 5: Reporting bugs -->
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-6 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
          <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/30 text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-400 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">5</span>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Reporting Issues</h2>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 ml-11">
          <li>• Click the 🐛 icon in the header to go to the <a href="/report-bug" class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 hover:underline">Bug Report</a> page.</li>
          <li>• Search for the affected converter, select severity, describe the issue, and submit.</li>
          <li>• Visit <a href="/vote-bugs" class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 hover:underline">Vote on Bug Fixes</a> to upvote bugs you want fixed first.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 6: Mobile -->
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-6 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
          <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/30 text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-400 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">6</span>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Mobile Usage</h2>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 ml-11">
          <li>• Tap the ☰ <strong>hamburger menu</strong> (top-left) to open the navigation sidebar.</li>
          <li>• The site is fully responsive — all converters work on phones and tablets.</li>
          <li>• You can add xConvert24 to your home screen for app-like access (PWA-ready).</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 7: Chat Assistant -->
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-6 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
          <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/30 text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-400 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">7</span>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Chat Assistant</h2>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 ml-11">
          <li>• Click the 💬 <strong>chat icon</strong> in the top header to open the assistant.</li>
          <li>• Type a question in natural language — e.g. "How do I convert kg to pounds?" or "I need a loan calculator".</li>
          <li>• The assistant searches across all 150+ units and tools and gives you direct links.</li>
          <li>• It also answers questions about how to use the site, dark mode, bug reporting, and more.</li>
          <li>• Click a suggested link to jump straight to that converter or tool.</li>
          <li>• Click the ✕ button or anywhere outside the panel to close it.</li>
          <li>• <strong>Tip:</strong> Try asking "help", "FAQ", "how do I use this site", or just type a unit name like "celsius" or "MPG".</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
